PushManagerUnregister.summary:
IMPORTANT Deprecated The unregister() method was used to ask the system to
unregister and delete the specified endpoint.

blockquote.para: Note: In the updated API, a subscription can be unregistered via the method.

PushManagerUnregister.returns:
A DOMRequest object to handle the success or failure of the method call.If the method call is successful, the request's result will be a
PushRegistration object representing the endpoint that has been
unregistered.
